history.content:
The adjustment period begins on Monday and right now the entire waitlist can fit into the class, if no one else uses up the reserved seats, so there's not a need to expand this class. Your chances are good, even if you're last on the waitlist. Of course, check to see that your lab is open.

Also, see https://eecs.berkeley.edu/resources/undergrads/eecs/degree-reqs/enrollment-policy
